## Verification Plan

### Automated Tests
- Test the `search_reddit` tool with specific queries to ensure it returns relevant thread links and snippets.
- Verify that the whitelisting logic in [src/index.ts](file:///Users/tahmidnur/.gemini/antigravity/scratch/theresidentialaddress/agents/gravity-claw/src/index.ts) correctly processes the updated `AUTHORIZED_TELEGRAM_USER_ID`.

### Manual Verification
1. **Team Member Test**: Have the new member send a message to `@asanbot` or `@markbtmbot` on Telegram and confirm they get a response.
2. **Reddit Strategy Run**: Ask Asan to "Generate daily Reddit lead report" and verify it drafts responses according to the "Value-First" strategy.
